N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4602.4 - Conditions for accepting application

State Regulations

No application shall be accepted unless it bears the
identification number assigned by the commission, is executed and verified and
is accompanied by the license fee of $25 for each scheduled games of chance
license period. Notes
